title: Grateful Dead Live at Robert F. Kennedy Stadium on 1989-07-12
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Adobe Audition CC 2015 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Minglewood Blues, Mississippi Half Step, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Far From Me, Cassidy, Friend Of The Devil, Promised Land

Set 2

Sugaree*, Women Are Smarter*, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Hey Jude Reprise-> Black Peter-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: Black Muddy River

* Bruce Hornsby, accordion on Sugaree and keyboards on Man Smart

reviews.review_text: Tasty! Very good sound through most of this show; just enough of the venue sounds, echo, etc. -- not a sterile soundboard. A solid mix -- thanks much Charlie!
